{"tid":1435153,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"炒太多咖哩唔舒服要飲涼茶","createTime":"2019-08-09T03:23:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-09T08:15:14.000Z","uid":220900,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"3ad20f7e356713fa583e30f9b33e6816f8592cf3","tid":1435153,"uid":220900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T03:23:47.000Z","msg":"呢排香城人鍾意炒咖哩，炒得多，唔多唔少個氣管、肺都會有啲唔舒服<br />\n有中醫朋友想介紹咗隻涼茶俾大家飲，可以舒緩到啲症狀，但真係好唔舒服都一定要去睇醫生呀<br />\n<br />\n魚腥草5錢<br />\n枇杷葉3錢<br />\n桔梗1錢<br />\n甘草2錢<br />\n<br />\n若體寒：如胃口差、女性來經期間則連杞子及玫瑰花同用（杞子1錢，玫瑰花1錢）<br />\n<br />\n用滾水泡10分鐘即可<br />\n<br />\n大家加油！<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">光復香港，時代革命</span>"},{"pid":"cead9819b18b0472d71828d0ff0185c49fbf5d00","tid":1435153,"uid":282624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T03:24:44.000Z","msg":"謝謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5727bf40faa93fa20f55530f040d50281960f180","tid":1435153,"uid":220900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T03:27:56.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"3ac1bfd0668e15930c6babcc2071a610b4e55a55","tid":1435153,"uid":221237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T03:33:25.000Z","msg":"養生"},{"pid":"3febb9fc2729abf93724ed5c744f0ae71301d981","tid":1435153,"uid":137043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T03:36:07.000Z","msg":"多謝你，要調理下身體先"},{"pid":"30e63578c44ea4e0206630af4ef9449b06a114e3","tid":1435153,"uid":220900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T05:09:14.000Z","msg":"推呀！"},{"pid":"f9eb15bf4ec6d09361fd8cbcdf1f3756eab91ecb","tid":1435153,"uid":218193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T05:11:24.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"f4753a30a91ee09c30f8ef54a6d70a36bab5dbbe","tid":1435153,"uid":220900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T08:15:14.000Z","msg":"Push"}]}